<title>Multimedia</title>

<p>Multimedia in GNOME is built on the <link xref="tech-gstreamer">GStreamer</link> framework. This allows simple playback of audio and video to complex non-linear editing. GStreamer uses <link xref="tech-pulseaudio">PulseAudio</link> when outputting audio, which allows it to target many types of output hardware.</p>

